	</docu>	
~]]></Comment><ReturnType>ULINT</ReturnType><ReturnBitSize>64</ReturnBitSize><Local><Name>StartCycleCount</Name><Type>ULINT</Type><BitSize>64</BitSize></Local><Properties><Property><Name>property</Name></Property></Properties></Method><Method><Name>__getLogger</Name><Comment><![CDATA[~
