~]]></Comment><BitSize>6656</BitSize><ExtendsType Namespace="TcoCore">TcoObject</ExtendsType><Implements Namespace="TcoCore">ITcoComponent</Implements><SubItem><Name>_inServiceMode</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>6592</BitOffs></SubItem><Method><Name>Service</Name><Comment><![CDATA[~
